SectionBody.Text: For the purposes of this part of chapter 112 the following words and phrases have the meanings ascribed to them in this section.

Subsection.Text: “Sending agency” means any department or agency of the federal government or a state government which sends any employee thereof to another government agency under this part.
“Receiving agency” means any department or agency of the federal government or a state government which receives an employee of another government under this part.
